mes5 <- base$Month == 5

dadosMes5 <- base[ mes5 ,]

#mean(base$Temp)

g <- ggplot( dadosMes5 , aes(  Wind ,Temp)  ) 

g + geom_point()

mes7 <- base$Month == 7

dadosMes7 <- base[ mes7 ,]

#mean(base$Temp)

g <- ggplot( dadosMes7 , aes(  Wind ,Temp)  ) 

g + geom_point() + geom_line()

g <- ggplot( base , aes(  Wind ,Temp , colour = factor(Month))  ) 

g + geom_point() + geom_line() + facet_grid( . ~ Month )

g + geom_point() + geom_line() + facet_grid(  Month ~ .)
